Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,(OP)
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.20,0:00:04.50,OP,NTP,0,0,0,,ありがとうの言葉
Dialogue: 0,0:00:05.11,0:00:10.70,OP,NTP,0,0,0,,木漏れ日みたいで、いいね♪
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.27,0:00:25.76,OP,NTP,0,0,0,,空 雲 果てしない道
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.34,0:00:31.09,OP,NTP,0,0,0,,ちっちゃい存在同士 手を取り
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.39,0:00:35.99,OP,NTP,0,0,0,,もっと 壮大 夢見てもいいかい？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.38,0:00:40.92,OP,NTP,0,0,0,,なんて 寛大な 地球だい？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.13,0:00:46.00,OP,NTP,0,0,0,,そう、きっと特別な双眼鏡だって、ね
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.21,0:00:50.87,OP,NTP,0,0,0,,探した景色は見つからない
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.20,0:00:55.50,OP,NTP,0,0,0,,世界で一番の絶景ポイントは
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.71,0:01:03.08,OP,NTP,0,0,0,,いつも目の前の「その笑顔」だったから
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.28,0:01:08.16,OP,NTP,0,0,0,,ありがとう いつもとなりにいてくれて
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.37,0:01:13.16,OP,NTP,0,0,0,,それだけでもう何もいらなかったよ
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.34,0:01:19.08,OP,NTP,0,0,0,,なかなか素直に言えないこの気持ちあふれて
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.15,0:01:24.64,OP,NTP,0,0,0,,今日もコハルビヨリだ いいね♪
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.20,0:00:04.50,OP,NTP,0,0,0,,一句「謝謝你」
Dialogue: 0,0:00:05.11,0:00:10.70,OP,NTP,0,0,0,,就像掠過樹梢的陽光 讚♪
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.27,0:00:25.76,OP,NTP,0,0,0,,藍天 白雲 漫漫長路
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.34,0:00:31.09,OP,NTP,0,0,0,,同樣渺小的存在 只要手牽著手
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.39,0:00:35.99,OP,NTP,0,0,0,,就能心懷更壯大的夢想？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.38,0:00:40.92,OP,NTP,0,0,0,,地球多麼寬大
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.13,0:00:46.00,OP,NTP,0,0,0,,沒錯 就算特製的望遠鏡
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.21,0:00:50.87,OP,NTP,0,0,0,,也找不到心中的景色
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.20,0:00:55.50,OP,NTP,0,0,0,,因為世界上最棒的景點
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.71,0:01:03.08,OP,NTP,0,0,0,,就是時刻綻放在眼前的那份笑容
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.28,0:01:08.16,OP,NTP,0,0,0,,謝謝你陪伴我身邊
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.37,0:01:13.16,OP,NTP,0,0,0,,有你相伴 別無所求
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.34,0:01:19.08,OP,NTP,0,0,0,,充滿心中的這份心情 總是說不出口
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.15,0:01:24.64,OP,NTP,0,0,0,,今天也是暖和的小陽春 讚♪
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.97,0:01:29.68,staff,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(1000,0)}翻譯：dgwxx／其他：cunhan
Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,(main)
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.53,0:01:34.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,和日向一起攀登回憶中的山峰谷川岳
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.66,0:01:36.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這個約定變成了現實
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.64,0:01:41.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是 下一個約定已經在等著我們了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.31,0:01:45.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,明天是飯能納涼煙火大會
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.87,0:01:51.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在谷川岳認識的末明來找我們玩 我們約好一起看煙火
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.42,0:01:55.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,雖然心中充滿期待…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.70,0:01:57.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小葵 快道歉！
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.78,0:02:00.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,該道歉的是日向你才對吧！
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.44,0:02:02.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小葵什麼事都怪到我身上！
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.03,0:02:05.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你才是 別把責任都推到我身上
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.78,0:02:08.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,說到底都怪你興趣太悶了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.54,0:02:10.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以才交不到男朋友
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.83,0:02:13.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,人家的興趣要你管！
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.34,0:02:16.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看看你自己 不也是沒有男朋友嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.60,0:02:18.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有沒有男朋友沒關係！
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.92,0:02:21.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是沒有男朋友的你先提這件事的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.41,0:02:23.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你這個笨蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.01,0:02:25.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你才笨蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.18,0:02:34.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不道歉就再也不理你了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.02,0:02:37.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這句話原句奉還！
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.87,0:02:41.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這次我可是真的生氣了！
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.76,0:02:46.27,title,NTP,0,0,0,,再見 我們的夏天
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.04,0:02:58.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這個日向 還不找我道歉
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.92,0:03:00.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你好
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.03,0:03:02.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 末明
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.82,0:03:05.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,歡迎 歡迎來飯能
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.06,0:03:11.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,別客氣 別客氣
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.12,0:03:14.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,高崎到飯能 一路上不無聊嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.46,0:03:18.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,光看著車窗外的景色就很高興了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.65,0:03:19.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那就好
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.22,0:03:22.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,今天真熱啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.30,0:03:25.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不過 多虧是晴天
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.59,0:03:28.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,群馬醬…？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.81,0:03:30.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,夢馬
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.62,0:03:33.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他是夢馬君
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.38,0:03:34.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可可娜醬的情人呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.49,0:03:37.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,夢馬
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.29,0:03:40.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這是飯能銀座
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.31,0:03:43.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我打工的地方就在前面
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.42,0:03:54.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.53,0:03:56.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 不好意思
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.50,0:03:59.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,其實剛跟日向吵完架
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.68,0:04:01.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,吵架…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.73,0:04:06.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,錯的當然是日向了 她卻一句道歉的話都沒有
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.25,0:04:08.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,發生什麼事了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.05,0:04:11.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你評評理 日向啊她把我的…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.62,0:04:12.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 是雪村同學
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.30,0:04:15.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,荒井老師
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.87,0:04:16.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,老師好
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.67,0:04:19.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你是…幾年級的？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.27,0:04:23.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,末明從群馬縣的高崎來玩的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.24,0:04:25.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這是我的班導師荒井老師
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.39,0:04:27.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,老師好
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.47,0:04:30.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這樣啊 飯能可好啦
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.73,0:04:31.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要玩得高興喔
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.49,0:04:34.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不如老師帶你玩好啦！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.54,0:04:36.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不 不麻煩您了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.05,0:04:40.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一直拍什麼呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.80,0:04:44.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,歷史建築 傳統倉庫…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.61,0:04:45.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,很有趣
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.73,0:04:49.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真的嗎 平時看習慣了不覺得特別呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.98,0:04:50.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看一下
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.71,0:04:53.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看起來好新鮮
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.43,0:04:58.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,換一個角度 看到的景色就會變得不一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.72,0:04:59.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這樣啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.93,0:05:01.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,末明好厲害
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.63,0:05:08.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這間蛋糕店就是我打工的地方
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.43,0:05:09.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小葵！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.83,0:05:14.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小光姐 真不好意思 店裡這麼忙我還請假
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.12,0:05:16.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,沒關係沒關係
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.53,0:05:18.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,今天不是有朋友來玩嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.95,0:05:21.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什麼 你說的朋友難道是男朋友嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.12,0:05:23.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不是啦
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.58,0:05:25.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什麼 小葵的男朋友
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.36,0:05:26.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎麼連店長都來了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.72,0:05:28.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,得趕緊告訴你媽媽…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.45,0:05:30.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,末明可是女孩子
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.44,0:05:30.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,咦
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.97,0:05:32.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,您好
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.32,0:05:33.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哎呀
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.31,0:05:35.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不好意思啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.73,0:05:37.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,歡迎來飯能
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.64,0:05:39.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊對了 等一下啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.04,0:05:45.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真走運啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.91,0:05:47.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大家人真好
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.03,0:05:49.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你常來這裡嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.02,0:05:52.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,放學後在這裡聊天什麼的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.49,0:05:56.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,對了對了 上次在台階那裡也跟日向吵架了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.39,0:06:00.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,她把我的裙子扯下來呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.29,0:06:01.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不覺得她很過分嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.01,0:06:03.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這還真過分…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.15,0:06:08.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不過那之後我也把她的裙子扯下來了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.29,0:06:10.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好過分…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.41,0:06:13.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這就是煙火大會的會場
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.29,0:06:17.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,之前跟大伙一起在這裡野餐呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.20,0:06:21.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,都怪日向 我還掉到河裡了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.75,0:06:29.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小時候從格子爬梯上摔下來過
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.57,0:06:31.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,之後就得了懼高症
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.63,0:06:34.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯 都怪日向
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.97,0:06:36.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 這不關她的事
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.31,0:06:38.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯 說到這 你看
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.66,0:06:40.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那就是天覽山
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.30,0:06:50.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,景色不錯吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.32,0:06:54.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,天氣好的時候 還能看到東京晴空塔和富士山呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.76,0:06:59.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這是我和日向爬的第一座山
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.12,0:07:05.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在這裡和日向喝茶 還吃了三明治
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.09,0:07:08.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小葵一直在談日向呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.88,0:07:11.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你們兩個真要好啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.75,0:07:13.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,才沒這回事呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.57,0:07:18.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,末明說得沒錯
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.06,0:07:22.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,飯能到處都是和日向的回憶
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.63,0:07:29.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這次都怪她才吵架的 但我也有一點點錯…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.52,0:07:33.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我還是跟她道個歉吧…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.34,0:07:35.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.43,0:07:37.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我跟她和好去
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.77,0:07:39.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.76,0:07:42.28,*Default,,0,0,0,,悄悄地
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.70,0:07:48.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小葵今天沒來打工嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.48,0:07:53.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真是的 都不跟我聯絡 都不知道她去哪裡了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.32,0:07:54.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,日向？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.56,0:07:57.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真的是日向啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.00,0:08:00.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你好
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.03,0:08:02.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小葵今天沒來喔
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.06,0:08:04.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看起來是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.80,0:08:06.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你就是日向啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.75,0:08:09.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,常聽小葵提到你喔
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.13,0:08:11.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大概能想到她怎麼貶我的…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.93,0:08:14.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小時候摔到水溝裡什麼的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.47,0:08:16.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,暗戀被你曝光什麼的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.99,0:08:18.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,聽說你還挺粗線條的？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.29,0:08:20.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這個臭小葵！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.57,0:08:21.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不不 還有啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.95,0:08:24.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,成績好 還會照顧人
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.12,0:08:27.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,做什麼事都很積極
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.39,0:08:30.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,說有好多地方要向你學習呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.91,0:08:44.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這次都怪她才吵架的 但我也有一點點錯…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.05,0:08:48.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,算了 這次還是跟她道個歉吧…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.07,0:08:56.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,雖然是小葵換下來的 不過尺寸剛好合身呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.66,0:08:57.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,謝謝阿姨
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.08,0:08:58.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那我們出發吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.30,0:09:13.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,事到臨頭還真是難開口啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.60,0:09:16.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我先開口道歉有點不甘心呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.89,0:09:19.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,她怎麼不先開口道歉
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.04,0:09:23.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,按道理不是應該你先開口道歉嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.85,0:09:25.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大家久等了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.30,0:09:27.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,學姐久等了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.81,0:09:29.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,末明 歡迎來飯能
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.78,0:09:30.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,學姐好
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.70,0:09:34.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,第一次看小楓學姐穿浴衣呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.06,0:09:37.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是友香幫我選的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.92,0:09:39.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真的很合身啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.06,0:09:40.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,對吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.83,0:09:41.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,對吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.96,0:09:45.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那我們出發吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.39,0:09:55.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,金魚先生 我來了喔
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.48,0:09:56.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,加油啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.88,0:10:00.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,剛才這招叫飛魚！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.90,0:10:02.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,接下來是尾鰭切！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.16,0:10:05.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,月牙落！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.98,0:10:08.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,登龍門！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.09,0:10:14.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我…我說啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.59,0:10:15.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小葵\N日向
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.86,0:10:16.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,給
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.59,0:10:19.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,撈到了這麼多呢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.90,0:10:22.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可可娜醬好厲害
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.73,0:10:24.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,接下來去挑戰釣水球
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.46,0:10:45.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,快開始了喔
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.19,0:10:55.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那個…日向…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.28,0:10:57.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我說…小葵…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.51,0:11:01.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,對不起！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.11,0:11:22.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,夢馬
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.26,0:11:34.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什麼 你們吵架了？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.50,0:11:36.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,沒發現啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.58,0:11:38.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,跟平時沒兩樣呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.61,0:11:39.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.68,0:11:41.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你們平時就那樣的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.90,0:11:44.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎麼吵起來的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.38,0:11:46.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,很無聊的事情啦
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.26,0:11:47.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,日向啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.34,0:11:49.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什麼 不是我 是你才對吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.11,0:11:51.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什麼嘛 是你才對
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.49,0:11:53.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,咦
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.34,0:11:54.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是你…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.22,0:11:56.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.98,0:11:59.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我們為什麼吵架呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.81,0:12:07.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我們的夏天 每天都很高興
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.56,0:12:13.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,願寶貴的每一天 直到永遠
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.94,0:12:17.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,對 明天 後天 永遠！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.26,0:12:19.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Yahoo!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.19,0:12:21.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,劇終
Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,(ED)
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.05,0:12:03.61,OP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8\fs32}晴れた日も 雨の日も しあわせだったら
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.89,0:12:07.12,OP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8\fs32}天気予報はいらないね
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.85,0:12:11.53,OP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8\fs32}また明日 あたらしい 空に描こう
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.74,0:12:15.48,OP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8\fs32}消えない Rainbow
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.01,0:12:26.47,OP,NTP,0,0,0,,紙と色鉛筆だけで
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.89,0:12:30.33,OP,NTP,0,0,0,,どんな夢も叶えられた
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.74,0:12:34.16,OP,NTP,0,0,0,,子供の頃の気持ち
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.62,0:12:37.98,OP,NTP,0,0,0,,取り戻したような日々
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.20,0:12:46.41,OP,NTP,0,0,0,,楽しかった季節ひつとが終わる
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.03,0:12:54.58,OP,NTP,0,0,0,,まっしろなスケジュール 落書きで埋めよう
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.64,0:13:00.21,OP,NTP,0,0,0,,12色パレットじゃ描けない世界
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.47,0:13:03.60,OP,NTP,0,0,0,,心に焼き付いているよ
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.31,0:13:08.05,OP,NTP,0,0,0,,好きな人100人にいつか見せたい
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.31,0:13:11.53,OP,NTP,0,0,0,,花咲く足あと
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.20,0:13:15.82,OP,NTP,0,0,0,,晴れた日も 雨の日も 幸せだったら
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.07,0:13:19.35,OP,NTP,0,0,0,,天気予報はいらないね
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.00,0:13:23.69,OP,NTP,0,0,0,,軽やかに 歩き出す 道の向こうに
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.93,0:13:27.73,OP,NTP,0,0,0,,心色 Rainbow
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.05,0:12:03.61,OP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8\fs32}無論晴天還是雨天 如果都有幸福
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.89,0:12:07.12,OP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8\fs32}就不需要天氣預報了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.85,0:12:15.48,OP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8\fs32}在明天新的晨光中畫下永不褪色的彩虹
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.01,0:12:30.33,OP,NTP,0,0,0,,只用紙和彩鉛 就能實現所有願望
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.74,0:12:37.98,OP,NTP,0,0,0,,每一天都彷彿重拾兒時的心意
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.20,0:12:46.41,OP,NTP,0,0,0,,愉快的季節告一段落
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.03,0:12:54.58,OP,NTP,0,0,0,,用塗鴉填滿雪白的日程表
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.64,0:13:03.60,OP,NTP,0,0,0,,十二色的調色板 畫不盡的世界 永遠烙在心裡
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.31,0:13:08.05,OP,NTP,0,0,0,,總有一天 分享給100個我愛的人
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.31,0:13:11.53,OP,NTP,0,0,0,,鮮花盛開的足跡
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.20,0:13:15.82,OP,NTP,0,0,0,,無論晴天還是雨天 如果都有幸福
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.07,0:13:19.35,OP,NTP,0,0,0,,就不需要天氣預報了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.00,0:13:27.73,OP,NTP,0,0,0,,輕快地邁開腳步 道路的遠方 是心中的彩虹
